(42, 6, 48, 19, 62, 2, 2, 'foundation on a rock', 'Foundation and Stability in Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of a strong foundation in faith. Luke describes a house built on a rock, while Psalms identifies God as a rock and defense, suggesting stability in times of trouble.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
