(42, 6, 48, 65, 1, 24, 24, 'founded upon a rock', 'Foundation and Stability in Faith', 'This connection highlights the theme of stability in faith. Both passages emphasize the idea of being secure and unshakeable, with Luke referencing a house founded on a rock and Jude speaking of being kept from falling.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
